Sentencas: This study suggests a new optimized model for optimum identification of the unknown variables in a Solid Oxide (SO) fuel cell.

Sentencas: The metaheuristic is based on a new improved model of a new metaheuristic, called the Red Fox Optimization Algorithm (IRFO).

Sentencas: To assess the method's accuracy and its consistency, it is validated by various pressure and temperature functional conditions.
